_sText:
This map is a MUST HAVE. it is so fun to play on especially if u love to KNIFE. knifing ontop the pyramid is honestly one of the most fun things ive done playing css because it brings a whole new element to knifing.

The map has all custom textures of heiroglyphics and ancient egyptian gods. the map has 40 spaun points 20 on each side. no matter how many players you have it plays amazing.

please i encourage your to download and play it one time and i garentee you will be hooked on it. 

please let me know the ip of your server so i can stop by sometime.

the map name came from the bible and the book of exodus. which is where the pharoah painting came from. oh yeah shoot the pharoah to go inside the bottom floor.
